&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 2&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47974256</guid><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 12:56:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Show HN: Stanzio, AI presentation tool that designs each slide as real HTML</title><link>https://stanzio.fly.dev/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Given that PowerPoint's format doesn't play well with LLMs, I built a tool that generates presentations as real HTML instead. Think Lovable but for slides. Would love to hear what you think :)&lt;/p&gt;
